data.description: A good, solid, well built Bi-level home w/over 2,500 sq. ft. of living area; 4 bedrooms; 2 baths, large living room; lower level family room w/additional wet bar area; oversized 2-car detached garage. Home is owned by the Welch Family who were in the house moving business. The original upper part of the home built in 1903 was placed on the lower level in the late 70's. Interior finish needs updating. Also option to purchase adjacent Lot to the North of Subject Property.
